      <title>沙特财政部长警告地缘政治是首要经济风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/saudi-finance-minister-says-geopolitics-world-economy-s-top-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯财政部长警告说，地缘政治可能是已经面临增长放缓和利率上升的世界经济最大的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/saudi-finance-minister-says-geopolitics-world-economy-s-top-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 07:38:17 GMT</pubDate>
