      <title>中国间谍重磅炸弹后德国选择党失去阵地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/german-spying-far-right-party-loses-ground-after-china-revelations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧洲议会选举的一项新民意调查中，极右翼德国另类选择党的支持率下降了两个百分点，这表明与中国情报部门有联系的指控正在损害该党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/german-spying-far-right-party-loses-ground-after-china-revelations</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 06:54:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克拒绝在当地投票前确认选举日期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/sunak-refuses-to-confirm-election-date-ahead-of-regional-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相拒绝在本周关键地区投票之前确定大选日期，这些投票被视为保守党前景的风向标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/sunak-refuses-to-confirm-election-date-ahead-of-regional-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
