      <title>弹药爆炸造成20名柬埔寨士兵死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-27/urgent-20-cambodian-soldiers-killed-in-ammunition-explosion-at-a-military-base</link>
      <description><![CDATA[柬埔寨金边（美联社）——柬埔寨首相洪马内表示，周六下午，柬埔寨西南部一处基地发生弹药爆炸，造成 20 名士兵死亡，数人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-27/urgent-20-cambodian-soldiers-killed-in-ammunition-explosion-at-a-military-base</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 13:12:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>一些美国学校关闭营地，反战抗议者奋起反抗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-27/student-anti-war-protesters-dig-in-as-faculties-condemn-university-leadership-over-calling-police</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约（美联社）——周六，抗议以色列与哈马斯战争的学生在美国各地的大学校园里挖坑，数十名示威者被捕，一些大学在收到反犹太主义活动的报道后采取了关闭营地的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-27/student-anti-war-protesters-dig-in-as-faculties-condemn-university-leadership-over-calling-police</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 05:48:44 GMT</pubDate>
